This paper discusses the task of Opinion Mining, which falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also deals with classification algorithms, which can be categorized under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of problem transformation methods is also mentioned, which can be related to Cybernetics (cs.CY) and Signal Processing (cs.SI).
